main event: A series of photographs depicting unidentified flying objects taken in Southampton, New York in 1966.
interesting points: The document is titled 'File 11073' and is from the FOREIGN TECHNOLOGY DIVISION, AFSC., There are 7 photographs included in the report., The images primarily show bright, glowing, oval-shaped objects in a dark night sky., The photographs are marked as 'UNCLASSIFIED'., The report was created on October 30, 1966.
sighted object: bright, oval-shaped objects in the night sky
